# Changelog

0.5.3 - 2019.02.05
  Update version of 'wildriver' to address input issues.
  Add '-W' option for ignoring edge weights.

0.5.2 - 2017.06.13

0.5.1 - 2017.06.01
  Switch to using 'wildriver' instead of 'bowstring'.
  Update version of 'domlib'.

0.5.0 - 2016.03.31
  Converted to using dlthreads.
  Fixed configuration file to compile without warnings as default.
  Fixed miscellaneous C standard violations.

0.4.6 - 2014.10.26
  Added namespace preserving macros.
  Added INSTALL file.

0.4.5 - 2014.10.03
  Fixed possible bug for large number of edges (4 billion) but moderate amount 
    of vertices.
  Modified the binary to allow for input of vertex-interal edge weights.

0.4.4 - 2014.09.29
  Fixed issue floating point exception when the number of threads is greater
    than the number of vertices.
  Changed cluster output to be through Bowstring.

0.4.3 - 2014.09.15
  Implemented edge number tracking to properly handle floating point edge
    weights.

0.4.2 - 2014.08.27
  Improved stability of floating point edge weights.
  Modified print out to include statistics on cluster sizes.
  Changed library call to by default print nothing.

0.4.1 - 2014.08.06
  Added "--no-zlib" option to configure script.
  Lots of refactoring.
  Improved documentation of internal functions.

0.4.0 - 2014.07.11
  Added changelog.
  Switched from using 'make config' to using a 'configure' script.
  Compatibility fixes for new version of domlib.

